493
00:51:23.610 --> 00:51:27.450
You remember the thousands of Jews
who were deported from Lodz,


494
00:51:27.510 --> 00:51:28.660
the ones who disappeared.

495
00:51:30.550 --> 00:51:34.430
Last week 300 train cars of clothing
returned for sorting.


496
00:51:39.440 --> 00:51:40.510
What else, Jacob?

497
00:51:41.500 --> 00:51:44.610
We hear rumors they are building
another camp. Treblinka.


498
00:51:45.420 --> 00:51:49.420
Only 90 kilometers from Warsaw where
there are fake station platforms,


499
00:51:49.480 --> 00:51:50.650
underground bunkers.

500
00:51:52.510 --> 00:51:55.580
One thing they have not
constructed - barracks.


501
00:51:57.440 --> 00:52:02.570
No barracks, l do not understand.
Why no barracks?


502
00:52:02.630 --> 00:52:05.480
Mama, they do not...

503
00:52:05.540 --> 00:52:09.620
ln such a camp,
the only purpose is death.


504
00:52:15.620 --> 00:52:18.590
We need to find a way
to get you out of the Ghetto.


505
00:52:20.510 --> 00:52:24.430
Get out, you say! Get out how?
Get out to where?


506
00:52:26.510 --> 00:52:27.480
Papa,

507
00:52:29.440 --> 00:52:31.640
Irena has made
an offer for Karolyna.


508
00:52:33.480 --> 00:52:35.600
There is a convent in the countryside.

509
00:52:35.660 --> 00:52:41.550
