Karolyna we must accept.


515
00:53:03.460 --> 00:53:06.550
- l believe a convent is best.
- No, it must not be done.


516
00:53:07.500 --> 00:53:08.530
Chaim Rozenfeld!

517
00:53:10.440 --> 00:53:14.600
You have loved me since l was a little
girl in pigtails and after these


518
00:53:14.660 --> 00:53:17.510
many years you know very well

519
00:53:17.570 --> 00:53:21.490
an opinion from me
is not a suggestion.


520
00:53:40.620 --> 00:53:44.500
Next time,
when you come she will be prepared.


521
00:53:45.530 --> 00:53:48.520
Irena, the Underground knows
what you're doing.


522
00:53:48.580 --> 00:53:49.630
They want to help.

523
00:53:50.440 --> 00:53:53.450
There's a man you should speak to,
goes by the name Trojan.


524
00:53:53.510 --> 00:53:55.450
24 Zurawia Street.

525
00:53:55.570 --> 00:53:57.530
Zurawia, 24.

526
00:54:00.520 --> 00:54:03.550
For Karolyna, l promise,
l will do everything...


527
00:54:03.590 --> 00:54:06.480
We know that, Irena. We know.

528
00:54:20.430 --> 00:54:21.440
l'm Trojan.

529
00:54:21.500 --> 00:54:23.440
