530
00:54:23.500 --> 00:54:25.440
- Konrad Zegota.
- Why me? What do you know?


531
00:54:25.500 --> 00:54:27.500
You created an efficient network,
saved many children.


532
00:54:27.560 --> 00:54:29.620
So far no one has been betrayed
or exposed.


533
00:54:30.430 --> 00:54:32.430
We, with the Underground,
have a good deal of money,


534
