and contacts.
It could be a good arrangement.


535
00:54:35.530 --> 00:54:38.600
- This money, where does it come from?
- Polish government in exile in London.


536
00:54:38.660 --> 00:54:42.420
- To help Jews?
- Zegota exists only for that.


537
00:54:42.480 --> 00:54:44.540
- Who is Konrad Zegota?
- He does not exist.


538
00:54:44.600 --> 00:54:47.610
Which makes him hard to find,
especially for Germans


539
00:54:48.420 --> 00:54:49.570
who will never stop looking.

540
00:54:51.550 --> 00:54:52.640
What is your proposal?

541
00:54:53.570 --> 00:54:57.470
We will help you
rescue children. If you agree.


542
00:55:01.650 --> 00:55:03.450
l agree.

543
00:55:04.610 --> 00:55:08.450
