Aryan papers, work records.


544
00:55:08.500 --> 00:55:12.420
You'll get them while picking up
the linen from the laundry at Bracka street,


545
00:55:12.450 --> 00:55:14.450
near the Three Crosses Square.

546
00:55:14.480 --> 00:55:16.650
This will be our contact point.

547
00:55:36.600 --> 00:55:39.630
- Looks like we're back in business.
- Let me count.


548
00:55:40.620 --> 00:55:42.540
Look. Identification cards.

549
00:55:45.450 --> 00:55:47.530
Very good work. 
These will do.

550
00:56:01.470 --> 00:56:04.420
- What's going on?
- They're deporting adults and children.


551
00:56:04.460 --> 00:56:05.560
- Orphanages?
- Yes.


552
00:57:04.660 --> 00:57:05.630
Stefan.

553
00:57:52.600 --> 00:57:53.550
Stefan.

554
00:57:53.610 --> 00:57:56.620
You must get out.
Do it, for me, for the children.


555
00:57:57.570 --> 00:58:00.520
You must see and remember
and tell the world.


556
00:58:01.430 --> 00:58:03.430
- No.
- Go. Go on. Quickly.


557
00:58:03.490 --> 00:58:05.430
Now.
Go, go, quickly!


558
00:58:05.490 --> 00:58:06.640
You know how to do it.

559
00:58:10.660 --> 00:58:12.580
May God walk with you. Go! Go!

560
00:58:55.590 --> 00:58:57.530
Thanks be to God!

561
00:58:57.590 --> 00:58:59.510
