do anything about it.


563
00:59:05.610 --> 00:59:07.490
l've heard this news.

564
00:59:08.480 --> 00:59:09.530
Who told you?

565
00:59:11.430 --> 00:59:12.520
Your friend.

566
00:59:41.430 --> 00:59:44.560
Let's go son, don't be afraid
l'll hide you to keep you warm.


567
00:59:44.620 --> 00:59:46.460
Are you ok?

568
01:00:29.610 --> 01:00:32.460
- There is a chance today.
- Please, one more day, just one.


569
01:00:32.520 --> 01:00:34.500
Now it is possible,
tomorrow is uncertain.


570
01:00:36.600 --> 01:00:41.530
We can't do it now.
Please, one more day, just one.


571
01:00:43.450 --> 01:00:46.440
Now it's possible.
Tomorrow is uncertain.


572
01:00:46.600 --> 01:00:49.470
Tomorrow he will be ready,

573
