l promise.

574
01:01:03.550 --> 01:01:05.620
You mustn't lock the door.

575
01:01:05.650 --> 01:01:10.470
Jews who refuse to leave
the building will be executed.


576
01:01:10.500 --> 01:01:11.650
Run downstairs, run.

577
01:01:59.430 --> 01:02:01.510
No more courthouse entrance.

578
01:02:04.480 --> 01:02:05.530
A big problem.

579
