You need to get more rest.

581
01:02:34.640 --> 01:02:38.500
For Heaven's sake,
if l'd had a stroke, l'd be dead.


582
01:02:38.560 --> 01:02:42.440
l'm telling you, l got up too fast,
l fainted. That's all.


583
01:02:42.480 --> 01:02:44.600
