A little carpentry.

589
01:03:19.610 --> 01:03:20.660
What do you think?

590
01:03:22.440 --> 01:03:25.610
l feel a little bit confined.
l think l need to get out.


591
01:03:26.640 --> 01:03:29.610
lt's, it's not opening.
It's stuck.


592
01:03:30.420 --> 01:03:32.460
lt, it, hmm...

593
01:03:32.520 --> 01:03:34.420
Can you please try? Please.

594
01:03:34.480 --> 01:03:38.480
- It's stuck from the outside.
- No. Please, open it. Please.


595
01:03:51.490 --> 01:03:55.470
