01:04:49.550 --> 01:04:50.440
Jasio?

601
01:04:54.440 --> 01:04:55.510
Do you remember?

602
01:05:02.560 --> 01:05:05.530
l can't leave them. l will not.

603
01:05:05.590 --> 01:05:09.470
You, you have done a good thing,
Jasio, a very important thing


604
01:05:09.530 --> 01:05:12.560
and it may be hard to
understand but the future will


605
01:05:12.620 --> 01:05:15.450
