even more than now.


606
01:05:15.550 --> 01:05:18.440
Which is why
tomorrow you must save yourself.


607
01:05:18.500 --> 01:05:21.540
You know the coal room?
Where the Rabbis study?


608
01:05:24.600 --> 01:05:27.590
Two o'clock tomorrow my friend
