any of you.


613
01:06:00.620 --> 01:06:02.580
Yes, you will, l promise.

614
01:06:03.510 --> 01:06:08.440
No, you can't promise.
Nobody can promise anything any more!


615
01:06:10.460 --> 01:06:12.600
Darling. Darling, darling,

616
01:06:14.540 --> 01:06:16.580
l love you with all my heart.

617
01:06:17.550 --> 01:06:21.470
My love for you is so big and
strong it will never go away.


618
01:06:22.480 --> 01:06:23.650
lt will always be with you.

619
01:06:24.460 --> 01:06:29.570
Whenever you think of me, l will
be there, right over your shoulder.


620
01:06:29.630 --> 01:06:31.550
Forever and ever.

621
01:06:47.630 --> 01:06:49.590
- Your name?
- Aniela Procowna.


622
01:06:49.650 --> 01:06:51.650
- And where are you from?
- Krakow, Poland.


623
01:06:52.460 --> 01:06:54.520
But when l grow up l want
to live in Bavaria.


624
01:06:54.580 --> 01:06:56.560
My uncle says Germany
is much more beautiful...


625
01:06:56.620 --> 01:06:58.540
- Your name?
- Aniela Procowna.


626
01:06:58.600 --> 01:07:00.520
- And where are you from?
- Krakow, Poland.


