01:08:47.510 --> 01:08:48.520
Jasio?

640
01:08:55.570 --> 01:08:56.520
l know.

641
01:08:56.600 --> 01:08:58.600
Come. Come.

642
01:09:10.560 --> 01:09:11.550
Jasio!

