669
01:12:35.590 --> 01:12:37.530
Jasio, listen to me.

670
01:12:38.460 --> 01:12:40.600
Land on your elbows,
keep your head down.


671
01:12:40.660 --> 01:12:43.590
- Come with me.
- Keep your head down and stay


672
01:12:43.640 --> 01:12:46.480
still until you see the train is gone.

673
01:12:46.540 --> 01:12:47.550
l love you, Papa.

674
01:12:47.610 --> 01:12:50.630
Then you must run as fast
as you can into the trees.


675
01:12:51.450 --> 01:12:54.440
l love you, Papa. Please! Come with me.
l don't want to please!


676
01:12:54.500 --> 01:12:57.590
Shh. Shh! Be quiet! 
You must be brave.

677
01:12:59.530 --> 01:13:03.490
l can't! Papa! l can't.
Please come with me. Please.


678
01:13:03.550 --> 01:13:04.580
One.

679
01:13:04.620 --> 01:13:06.620
- No! Please!
- One, two.


680
01:13:07.440 --> 01:13:07.640
Papa!

681
01:13:08.580 --> 01:13:09.530
Three!

682
01:13:12.500 --> 01:13:13.490
