01:15:48.440 --> 01:15:50.500
Prima ballerina.

696
01:15:54.500 --> 01:15:55.530
l love you.

697
01:15:59.510 --> 01:16:00.520
Me too.

698
01:16:08.650 --> 01:16:09.660
Go on, now.

699
01:16:46.580 --> 01:16:49.490
Shouldn't you have taught
me this as a child?


700
01:16:49.550 --> 01:16:52.560
- Over and under.
- It's beautiful.


701
01:16:53.570 --> 01:16:56.630
- You are so mean.
