730
01:21:16.540 --> 01:21:19.430
We know you are not so involved
with these criminals.


731
01:21:19.470 --> 01:21:22.580
And if you tell us where to find
this man you will not be executed.


732
01:22:12.600 --> 01:22:13.630
Sendler, out!

