738
01:23:34.630 --> 01:23:36.660
l do what l'm told, that's all.

739
01:24:23.530 --> 01:24:24.580
Stefania?

740
01:24:25.550 --> 01:24:26.600
You're alive!

741
01:24:28.540 --> 01:24:31.620
l swear, l told them nothing.
