- You know l would never betray you.
- As a good soldier.


743
01:24:35.570 --> 01:24:38.420
- Yes.
- A good soldier.


744
01:24:40.600 --> 01:24:42.520
You have done very well.

745
01:24:45.510 --> 01:24:46.610
Everyone out! Out!

746
01:25:01.610 --> 01:25:02.560
Not you!

747
01:25:02.620 --> 01:25:04.560
No! No, wait. Wait!

748
01:25:17.630 --> 01:25:18.600
Aim!

749
01:25:19.630 --> 01:25:20.600
Fire!

750
01:25:23.460 --> 01:25:25.530
Get away from here! Go! Go!

751
01:25:27.640 --> 01:25:28.600
Go!

752
01:25:28.650 --> 01:25:32.460
But, l, l don't have
my identification card!


753
01:25:32.520 --> 01:25:36.420
Stupid woman! You are dead! With them.
Go! Run away! Get out!


754
01:25:57.660 --> 01:25:59.470
Irena!

755
01:26:05.650 --> 01:26:06.630
Viktor.

756
01:26:10.540 --> 01:26:14.500
They'll find out.
And they'll look for you.


757
01:26:15.570 --> 01:26:17.420
l'll be safe.

758
01:26:17.530 --> 01:26:21.440
Your mother is right,
your feet need a specialist.


759
01:26:21.490 --> 01:26:24.520
l know it's hard but please
try not to walk too much.


760
01:26:40.520 --> 01:26:41.570
Promise me...

761
01:26:43.590 --> 01:26:45.590
you won't come to my funeral.

762
01:26:48.600 --> 01:26:51.590
- Mama, don't say such things.
- Promise me.


763
01:26:57.590 --> 01:26:58.580
Irenka.

764
01:27:06.440 --> 01:27:07.620
Can l tell you something.

765
01:27:08.600 --> 01:27:09.610
l'm...

766
01:27:10.440 --> 01:27:11.450
proud...

767
01:27:11.510 --> 01:27:12.540
of you.

768
01:27:12.600 --> 01:27:13.590
Very proud

769
01:27:16.480 --> 01:27:18.560
So many l could not save.

770
01:27:20.450 --> 01:27:23.510
You've done a good and decent thing.

771
01:27:24.580 --> 01:27:27.490
ln this world that's not so bad.

772
01:27:29.430 --> 01:27:30.500
lt's time.

773
01:27:34.440 --> 01:27:36.560
We must be in the mountains
before dark.


774
01:27:42.580 --> 01:27:43.630
Mama.

775
01:27:46.580 --> 01:27:48.440
Don't worry,

776
01:27:49.430 --> 01:27:50.500
l'll be fine.

777
01:27:57.450 --> 01:27:58.480
Go.

778
01:28:23.630 --> 01:28:24.640
Wait, Irena.

779
01:28:25.610 --> 01:28:26.540
Trojan.

780
01:28:26.600 --> 01:28:28.600
Thank you so much for all
you've done.


781
01:28:28.660 --> 01:28:30.580
No. Thank you.

782
01:28:31.590 --> 01:28:35.490
There's something
Konrad Zegota must have.


783
01:28:39.550 --> 01:28:40.620
They're all here.

784
01:28:42.520 --> 01:28:43.610
Every child.

785
01:28:44.520 --> 01:28:46.540
Where we hid them.

786
01:28:47.490 --> 01:28:48.600
When all this is over,

787
01:28:49.470 --> 01:28:52.580
they must be returned
to whatever remains of their families.


788
01:28:52.660 --> 01:28:54.540
l will do it. l promise.

789
01:28:54.600 --> 01:28:55.650
Thank you.

790
01:29:15.510 --> 01:29:17.630
From now on you are Klara Dabrowska.

791
01:29:29.530 --> 01:29:33.450
Once upon a time,
there was a little girl


792
01:29:36.540 --> 01:29:39.450
l am so fond of stories
that begin that way.


793
01:29:53.450 --> 01:29:55.570
l have kielbasa, bread...

794
01:29:56.640 --> 01:29:58.560
- You like?
- Yes, l do.


795
01:29:58.620 --> 01:29:59.590
Good!

796
01:30:00.600 --> 01:30:05.450
- First, you must come meet my pigs.
- Really Piotr, that's not necessary.


797
01:30:08.640 --> 01:30:12.580
One thing l can say about town folk,
they make terrible farmers.


798
01:30:12.640 --> 01:30:14.480
Please, let me down.

799
01:30:32.440 --> 01:30:33.570
Oh, thank God.

800
01:30:41.490 --> 01:30:43.630
- Are you all right?
- Now, yes


801
01:30:59.430 --> 01:31:00.640
We must fight for what is good.

802
01:31:01.530 --> 01:31:03.570
Good must prevail.

803
01:31:04.640 --> 01:31:07.470
lt must prevail and l believe in this.

804
01:31:07.530 --> 01:31:09.570
As long as l'm alive...

805
01:31:09.630 --> 01:31:11.610
as long as l have strength...

806
01:31:12.500 --> 01:31:14.620
l will say good is best.

807
01:31:15.510 --> 01:31:16.560
Love,

808
01:31:16.620 --> 01:31:18.460
tolerance

809
01:31:19.470 --> 01:31:20.580
and humility

810
01:31:22.420 --> 01:31:23.550
- -that's it.